in the hot

22:42.461 --> 22:48.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
summer sunshine, his daughter
Reem in his
arms, and posted this picture on
Twitter.

22:48.400 --> 22:53.138 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It went viral, and soon there
was a campaign
to raise money for him, using
the hashtag

22:53.239 --> 23:03.282 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
#buypens. Its organizers hoped
to raise $5,000.
