$190,000.

23:03.382 --> 23:13.559 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, with that money, he bought
a bakery,
sandwich shop and a small
restaurant, and

23:13.659 --> 23:21.567 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
