refugees supporting
their families. His son even
helps out.

23:21.667 --> 23:27.906 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"My children's lives changed,"
he tells us.
"We were living in a room that
was uninhabitable.

23:28.007 --> 23:33.145 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But now we live in a house with
four rooms.
I have furnished it nicely. My
son goes to

23:33.245 --> 23:38.517 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
