after and is
learning. And I have three shops
and I'm working.

23:38.617 --> 23:41.854 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
My life has changed totally."

23:41.954 --> 23:47.126 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Abdul Halim is extremely lucky.
