pregnant and living on debt, she
is desperate

25:11.009 --> 25:12.845 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to join her husband.

25:12.945 --> 25:22.054 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
"Honestly, I have no more
strength. I'm tired,"
