money.

26:16.975 --> 26:20.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: Yes, they don't have
money to rent
apartments.

26:20.646 --> 26:26.785 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JANE FERGUSON: Bitter snowstorms
