43:52.797 --> 43:57.301 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
game vs. a rivalry team.
Physiologically,
athletes in a rivalry game,
testosterone levels

43:57.401 --> 44:01.272 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
are different. Saliva levels are
