45:35.766 --> 45:37.702 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
don't necessarily make good
coaches.

45:37.802 --> 45:39.670 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JON WERTHEIM: Right.

45:39.770 --> 45:43.507 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's funny. Ron Rivera and
