other qualities, right? This is
the face of

47:35.820 --> 47:40.024 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the franchise. This is the
leader. This is
one of the most important
positions in sports.

47:40.124 --> 47:44.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what we do, it's called the
halo effect,
where we have qualities that we
like in someone

47:44.328 --> 47:48.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and we conflate all sorts of
other qualities.
